T1158.long: To prevent normal users from accidentally changing special files on a system, most operating systems have the concept of a ‘hidden’ file. These files don’t show up when a user browses the file system with a GUI or when using normal commands on the command line. Users must explicitly ask to show the hidden files either via a series of Graphical User Interface (GUI) prompts or with command line switches (dir /a for Windows and ls –a for Linux and macOS).

strings: ONGC BLQ2 Offshore platform Mumbai offshore
TRANSOCEAN OFFSHORE INTERNATIONAL VENTURES LTD, MUMBAI, INDIA
Ultra- deepwater drillship GSF Explorer, ONGC Krishna Godavari basin block
Deepwater Semi Sub JACK BATES, East Coast India
Helicopter under water Escape & Sea Survival
Radio communication, crew change & administrative work at offshore.
Establishes and coordinates all radio communications.
Receives and transmits radio communications in accordance with applicable international regulations.
Responsible for continually updating POB and lifeboat lists as personnel movements take place.
Performs and coordinates isolation of radio equipment and transmissions during periods of radio silence.
Responsible for correspondence associated with helicopter operations, including radio communications with the heliport, weather, helicopters, passengers and cargo manifests.
Inspection and maintenance of radio equipment, associated batteries and antenna's.
Administration duties as instructed and directed by supervisor.
Organize crew change activities, accommodation, air and ground transportation.
communicate with vessels and tugs , watching channel 16 and marine channels, arrange pilot for berthing and un berthing vessels, maintain pob, maintaning reports etc.

OPERATE & MAINTAIN GMDSS EQUIPMENTS EFFICIENTLY. COMMUNICATE WITH BOATS, COAST STATIONS, CHOPPERS, BASE STATIONS AND MERCHANT SHIPS ON VHF & AERO VHF RADIOS FOR CARGO, CREW CHANGE MATTERS. SPEAK ENGLISH WELL. OPERATE MICROSOFT OUTLOOK & MS OFFICE EFFICIENTLY. HANDLE POB, ROOM ALLOTMENTS, MAINTAIN TIMESHEETS,
I here by declare that the above details are true and correct to by best of my
